item.title: Don't Miss Out on the Once-in-a-Lifetime Opportunity to See Boise's Parade of Homes 2022!
item.description: Don’t Miss Out on the Once-in-a-Lifetime Opportunity to See Boise’s Parade of Homes 2022! The Boise Parade of Homes is a one-of-a-kind event that offers attendees an opportunity to explore the latest in home design, construction, and technology From luxurious custom homes to log cabins, the Parade of Homes provides a unique look into the world of home building This year, the event will take place from June 4th to June 20th
